{
  "texts": [
    "AI/ML Model Lifecycle We model edge AI/ML models deployed at the edge as being in one of the following four states (see Figure 1): • Model Program Object.",
    "An AI/ML model begins its life in some state of training.",
    "Model Program Objects are often Python objects, are subject to training, and reside in a repository such as Github.",
    "• Model Serialized Object has undergone serialization for sharing, packaging into a container, etc.",
    "Serialized models are persisted in an object store, file system, etc."
  ]
}